		<description>'da deathskulls, or deth skulls, are an ork "klan" dat ‘as an unsavoury reputation as inveterate looters, scavengers, borrowers, an’ scroungaz. ‘da orks uv ‘da deathskull klan have a well-deserved reputation as dieves an’ filchaz. Neva ones ta teef dere fair share or spend teef when an item kan be spirited away wit' a modicum uv effort, da deathskulls are nearly as mistrusted among fellow orks as dere kousins da blood axes.
 
whereas da notoriety uv da blood axes iz kompletely without merit, da deathskulls deserve dere scabrous reputations ta an ork. When not loot'n bodiez on 'da battlefield (both ork an non-ork), dey kan be found eitha fight'n' or bicker'n among demselves for scavenged items, or steal'n everyth'n ‘dat iz not nailed down from wun annuver an any otha ork ‘n sight.
 
some uv wot dey steal dey trade or sell ta otha orks, or turn into upgraded wargear, but ‘da majority uv dere loot dey simply hoard. Anyth'n "'dat might kome 'n 'andy lata" iz put aside an kept 'n wun or more hidey holes, from useful items like weapons an armour ta trinkets, lucky charms, an strange gubbins uv unknown use or provenance.</description>
